OL,3,CAlcohol prices will rise with tax
OL,4,Chikes, industry bosses warn
OL,6,FWine and spirits bosses have warned
OL,7,Fthat firms "have no choice but to
OL,8,Fincrease prices" to stay afloat as an
OL,9,Fincrease in alcohol duty comes into
OL,10,Feffect.
OL,12,FIn November's budget, Chancellor
OL,13,FRachel Reeves confirmed that alcohol
OL,14,Fduty would increase in line with
OL,15,FRetail Price Index (RPI) inflation.
OL,17,FIt means that the tax charged on
OL,18,Falcoholic drinks will increase by
OL,19,F3.66% from Sunday, February 1.
