OL,3,CAlcohol prices will rise with tax
OL,4,Chikes, industry bosses warn
OL,6,FThe tax is directly levied upon
OL,7,Falcohol producers, but industry chiefs
OL,8,Fhave warned there will be a "trickle
OL,9,Fdown" effect to shoppers after
OL,10,Fwitnessing a number of other cost
OL,11,Fincreases in recent years.
OL,13,FData has shown that the changes would
OL,14,Fsee the duty on a typical bottle of
OL,15,Fgin, with 37.5% alcohol by volume
OL,16,F(ABV), increase by 38p to #8.98 after
OL,17,FVAT.
OL,19,FA bottle of Scotch whisky at 40% ABV
OL,20,Fwould see its duty increase by 39p to
OL,21,F#9.51.
