OL,3,CAlcohol prices will rise with tax
OL,4,Chikes, industry bosses warn
OL,6,FMeanwhile, a bottle of 14.5% red wine
OL,7,Fwill see its duty increase by 14p.
OL,9,FThe Wine and Spirit Trade Association
OL,10,F(WSTA) said the tax on a bottle of
OL,11,F14.5% red wine has gone up #1.10 a
OL,12,Fbottle since the recent alcohol duty
OL,13,Fregime was introduced in August 2023.
OL,15,FThe UK Spirits Alliance, which
OL,16,Frepresents hundreds of distillers
OL,17,Facross the UK, has written to the
OL,18,Fchancellor urging her to use an
OL,19,Fupcoming duty review to drive growth,
OL,20,Fend "spirits discrimination" and put
OL,21,Fin place a long-term approach.
