OL,3,CAlcohol prices will rise with tax
OL,4,Chikes, industry bosses warn
OL,6,FAlcohol duties are partly linked to
OL,7,Fthe strength of drinks, with beer
OL,8,Fbelow 3.5% ABV paying a significantly
OL,9,Flower level of tax following an
OL,10,Foverhaul of duties in 2023.
OL,12,FA number of beer brands, such as
OL,13,FFoster's, have reduced their strength
OL,14,Fto 3.4% in recent months in a bid to
OL,15,Freduce their duty costs.
OL,17,FThe duty on beer will increase on
OL,18,Fdrinks sold in both pubs and
OL,19,Fsupermarkets, with pubs impacted for
OL,20,Fthe first time since 2017.
