OL,3,CAlcohol prices will rise with tax
OL,4,Chikes, industry bosses warn
OL,6,FEmma McClarkin, chief executive of the
OL,7,FBritish Beer and Pub Association,
OL,8,Fsaid: "These changes unfortunately
OL,9,Fincrease the likelihood of further
OL,10,Fprice rises, which no brewer or
OL,11,Fpublican would want to inflict on
OL,12,Ftheir customers.
OL,14,F"For brewers, who already pay some of
OL,15,Fthe highest rates of beer duty in
OL,16,FEurope, this increase will add further
OL,17,Fstrain to their already razor-thin
OL,18,Fprofit margins and risk one of the
OL,19,FUK's world-renowned industries
OL,20,Fproducing the greatest beers in the
OL,21,Fworld."
